import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Switch,Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from '../rootComponents/Home'
import TutorialContent from '../rootComponents/TutorialContent'


const Router = () => {
  return(

    <BrowserRouter>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path='/kl' component={Home}/>
      <Route path='/tuto' component={TutorialContent}/>
    </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
export default Router
